## PATENT NOTICE

The PAR(2) (Phase-Amplitude-Relationship) methodology and associated statistical 
equations described in this software are the subject of a **pending patent 
application in the United Kingdom**. The patent covers the core hypothesis, 
mathematical formulations, and analytical methods used by this software.

**Territorial Scope**: The pending patent application is filed in the United Kingdom.
Patent protection may not extend to other jurisdictions. Users outside the UK should
consult with legal counsel regarding IP status in their jurisdiction. The authors
reserve the right to file additional patent applications in other territories.

