## SCIENTIFIC DISCLAIMER

PAR(2) is an exploratory statistical method for hypothesis generation. Results 
should be validated using peer-reviewed methods (JTK_CYCLE, MetaCycle, RAIN) 
and independent experiments before publication. See the application's Help 
documentation for cross-validation guidance.

